# Leo Database Schema

**Purpose**: Single source of truth for all Supabase tables in Leo.  
**Usage**: Reference before writing SQL migrations or TypeScript queries.

---

## Tables Overview

| # | Acronym | Table Name | Description |
|---|---------|------------|-------------|
| **Auth & Users** ||||
| 1 | MYSMK | `myday_safe_master_keys` | User master keys for Safe encryption (RSA) |
| 2 | MYUL | `myday_user_levels` | User subscription/access levels |
| **Safe (Encrypted)** ||||
| 3 | MYEE | `myday_encrypted_entries` | Encrypted password/credential entries |
| 4 | MYSSE | `myday_shared_safe_entries` | Shared password entries (group-based) |
| 5 | MYDV | `myday_document_vaults` | Encrypted documents in Safe |
| 6 | MYSSD | `myday_shared_safe_documents` | Shared documents (group-based) |
| 7 | MYBR | `myday_bank_records` | Encrypted financial records (FDs, accounts, bills) |
| 8 | MYGFM | `myday_group_finance_messages` | Group finance chat (FDs, alerts, docs) |
| **Groups & Sharing** ||||
| 9 | MYG | `myday_groups` | User-created sharing groups |
| 10 | MYGM | `myday_group_members` | Group membership records |
| 11 | MYGEK | `myday_group_encryption_keys` | RSA-encrypted group AES keys |
| **My Lists (TODOs)** ||||
| 12 | MYTG | `myday_todo_groups` | User-created TODO lists |
| 13 | MYTI | `myday_todo_items` | Individual TODO items |
| 14 | MYSTG | `myday_shared_todo_groups` | Shared TODO lists |
| 15 | MYST | `myday_shared_todos` | Shared TODO items |
| **Tasks & Routines** ||||
| 16 | MYTSK | `myday_tasks` | Daily tasks/routines |
| 17 | MYTC | `myday_task_completions` | Task completion records |
| **Calendar & Events** ||||
| 18 | MYE | `myday_events` | Calendar events |
| 19 | MYSE | `myday_shared_events` | Shared calendar events |
| 20 | MYNBD | `myday_notifybeforedays` | Notification preferences |
| 21 | MYRD | `myday_reference_days` | Reference calendar (holidays) |
| **Calendar Enrichments** ||||
| 22 | MYCE | `myday_calendar_enrichments` | Rich holiday data (core) |
| 23 | MYCF | `myday_calendar_facts` | Facts about holidays |
| 24 | MYCS | `myday_calendar_statistics` | Statistics for holidays |
| 25 | MYCTIP | `myday_calendar_tips` | Tips and reminders |
| 26 | MYCTI | `myday_calendar_timeline_items` | Timeline/countdown items |
| 27 | MYCQI | `myday_calendar_quick_ideas` | Quick activity ideas |
| 28 | MYCER | `myday_calendar_external_resources` | External links |
| 29 | MYCA | `myday_calendar_action_items` | Action buttons |
| **Journal & Resolutions** ||||
| 30 | MYJE | `myday_journal_entries` | Journal entries |
| 31 | MYR | `myday_resolutions` | New Year resolutions |
| **Lists & Items** ||||
| 32 | MYI | `myday_items` | Multi-category items (Gift Cards, Warranty, Notes, Subscription) |
| 33 | MYRT | `myday_routines` | User routines |
| **Collaboration** ||||
| 34 | MYEC | `myday_entry_comments` | Comments on shared entries |
| 35 | MYCM | `myday_comment_mentions` | @mentions in comments |
| 36 | MYCR | `myday_comment_reactions` | Emoji reactions |
| 37 | MYCT | `myday_comment_templates` | Saved comment templates |
| **Tags** ||||
| 38 | MYTAGS | `myday_tags` | User tags and system categories |
| **Voice / AI** ||||
| 39 | MYVCL | `myday_voice_command_logs` | Voice command transcripts, parsed intent (`detected_category`), entities, outcomes |

